    "body" : "<p>I also experienced the same problem. It has to do with the computer memory, that means your AVD or emulator is too big for your computer. Your computer cannot handle your emulator/AVD.  Best solution is to connect a real Android device to your computer and run your application. That worked for me.</p>\n"
